Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.60,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}変わる世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:40.60,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}瞬息万变的世上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.88,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}鐘が響くゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:44.88,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}钟声回响耳边
